      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will likely require significant work or serve as a parts car. The engine currently struggles to stay running and has a major oil leak, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. The body has extensive rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling across the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn, several electronic components are non-functional, and there is a persistent musty odor. It is recommended that any potential buyer brings a trailer for transport.",
