    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are honored to present this exemplary vehicle, which remains in pristine, showroom-state condition. Meticulously preserved and showing no discernible signs of previous ownership, this specimen serves as a benchmark for the model's lineage. It has been subjected to a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our uncompromising standards for mechanical and aesthetic excellence. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of peerless caliber.",
      "price": 48900.0,
