      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that pristine, new-car feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
