    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit boasts a meticulously maintained VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement, channeling torque through a pristine limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to maintain structural integrity under high-torque loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, and the exterior displays original paint depth with zero oxidation. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key example for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
